flowchart TD
    Start([Lambda processQueja<br/>recibe mensaje de SQS]) --> Idempotency{Check<br/>idempotencia}
    Idempotency -->|Ya procesado| Skip[Skip - ACK mensaje]
    Idempotency -->|Nuevo| Validate{Input valido?<br/>Zod schema}

    Validate -->|No| BadRequest[Log error +<br/>ir a DLQ]
    Validate -->|Si| GetAdj{Tiene<br/>adjuntos?}

    GetAdj -->|Si PDF/Imagen| DocAI[OCI Document<br/>Understanding]
    GetAdj -->|No| PromptBuild
    DocAI --> ExtractText[Extraer texto]
    ExtractText --> PromptBuild

    PromptBuild[Construir prompt<br/>estructurado] --> CB1{Circuit Breaker<br/>cerrado?}

    CB1 -->|Si - intentar| Cohere[Cohere Command R<br/>30s timeout]
    CB1 -->|No - skip| Llama

    Cohere --> ValidateOut1{Output valido?<br/>Zod parse}
    ValidateOut1 -->|Si| Save[Guardar en DynamoDB<br/>status=ANALIZADA]
    ValidateOut1 -->|No| Retry1{Reintentar?}
    Retry1 -->|Si| Cohere
    Retry1 -->|No, attempts>=3| DLQ[Enviar a DLQ]

    Save --> EmitEvent[Emitir evento<br/>queja.analizada]
    EmitEvent --> End([Fin - ACK SQS])

    Cohere -->|Timeout/Error| LlamaCheck{Circuit cerrado?}
    LlamaCheck -->|Si| Llama[Llama 3.1 70B<br/>30s timeout]
    LlamaCheck -->|No| CommandPlus

    Llama --> ValidateOut2{Output valido?}
    ValidateOut2 -->|Si| Save
    ValidateOut2 -->|No| Retry2{Attempts<3?}
    Retry2 -->|Si| Llama
    Retry2 -->|No| DLQ

    Llama -->|Timeout/Error| CommandPlus[Cohere Command R+<br/>30s timeout]
    CommandPlus --> ValidateOut3{Output valido?}
    ValidateOut3 -->|Si| Save
    ValidateOut3 -->|No| Default[Respuesta controlada<br/>fallback final]
    Default --> Save

    CommandPlus -->|Timeout/Error| Default

    Save --> End

    classDef startEnd fill:#10B981,stroke:#059669,color:#fff,stroke-width:2px
    classDef decision fill:#F59E0B,stroke:#D97706,color:#fff
    classDef error fill:#EF4444,stroke:#B91C1C,color:#fff
    classDef model fill:#2563EB,stroke:#1E40AF,color:#fff
    classDef success fill:#3B82F6,stroke:#1E40AF,color:#fff

    class Start,End startEnd
    class Idempotency,Validate,GetAdj,CB1,ValidateOut1,ValidateOut2,ValidateOut3,LlamaCheck,Retry1,Retry2 decision
    class BadRequest,DLQ error
    class Cohere,Llama,CommandPlus model
    class Save,EmitEvent,Default,DocAI,ExtractText,PromptBuild,Skip success
